Package edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.model.rescue

Class Rescue

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.packdoption.model.rescue.Rescue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Rescue>
    public class Rescue
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Rescue>
    Class to represent a rescue. Each rescue has a name, a list of Animals who are part of the rescue, and a list of Animals that are waiting to see the veterinarian.
    Author:
    bmrowan, mlee25
